            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Esta lista contiene películas como <code>\"Vertigo\"</code> y fechas de estreno como <code>1958</code>, pero no está claro qué fecha pertenece a qué película.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movies = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Vertigo\"</code> seguido de <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 88424,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos agrupar piezas de datos relacionadas con una <strong>tupla</strong>, como en <code>movie_tuples</code> aquí, que agrupa nombres de películas y fechas de estreno juntas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movies = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"movie_tuples = [(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"), (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")]\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option startIndex=\"79\" endIndex=\"80\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>(\"Vertigo\", 1958)</code> seguido de <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Tuples",
            "id": 88353,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><strong>Tuplas</strong> nos ayudan a agrupar diferentes piezas de datos que pertenecen juntas, como en la tupla <code>vertigo_data</code> aquí.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"vertigo_data = (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(vertigo_data)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"('Vertigo', 1958)\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>vertigo_data</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parentheses",
            "id": 88354,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Creemos tuplas de manera similar a las listas, pero usamos paréntesis <code>()</code> en lugar de corchetes alrededor de los valores.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"vertigo_data = (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(vertigo_data)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"32\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\",\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"('Vertigo', 1958)\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>(</code> seguido de <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
